tags[name,description]:
  actions	Endpoints to manage GitHub Actions using the REST API.
  activity	Activity APIs provide access to notifications, subscriptions, and timelines.
  apps	Information for integrations and installations.
  billing	Monitor charges and usage from Actions and Packages.
  checks	Rich interactions with checks run by your integrations.
  code-scanning	Retrieve code scanning alerts from a repository.
  codes-of-conduct	Insight into codes of conduct for your communities.
  emojis	List emojis available to use on GitHub.
  dependabot	Endpoints to manage Dependabot.
  dependency-graph	Endpoints to access Dependency Graph features.
  gists	View, modify your gists.
  git	Raw Git functionality.
  gitignore	View gitignore templates
  issues	Interact with GitHub Issues.
  licenses	View various OSS licenses.
  markdown	Render GitHub flavored Markdown
  merge-queue	Interact with GitHub Merge Queues.
  meta	Endpoints that give information about the API.
  migrations	Move projects to or from GitHub.
  oidc	Endpoints to manage GitHub OIDC configuration using the REST API.
  orgs	Interact with organizations.
  packages	Manage packages for authenticated users and organizations.
  pulls	Interact with GitHub Pull Requests.
  rate-limit	Check your current rate limit status.
  reactions	Interact with reactions to various GitHub entities.
  repos	Interact with GitHub Repos.
  search	Search for specific items on GitHub.
  secret-scanning	Retrieve secret scanning alerts from a repository.
  teams	Interact with GitHub Teams.
  users	Interact with and view information about users and also current user.
  code-quality	Insights into reliability, maintainability, and efficiency of your codebase.
  codespaces	Endpoints to manage Codespaces using the REST API.
  copilot	Endpoints to manage Copilot using the REST API.
  copilot-spaces	Endpoints to manage Copilot Spaces using the REST API.
  security-advisories	Manage security advisories.
  interactions	Owner or admin management of users interactions.
  classroom	Interact with GitHub Classroom.
  desktop	Desktop specific endpoints.
  enterprise-teams	Endpoints to manage GitHub Enterprise Teams.
  enterprise-team-memberships	Endpoints to manage GitHub Enterprise Team memberships.
  enterprise-team-organizations	Endpoints to manage GitHub Enterprise Team organization assignments.
  code-security	Endpoints to manage Code security using the REST API.
  private-registries	Manage private registry configurations.
  hosted-compute	Manage hosted compute networking resources.
  credentials	Revoke compromised or leaked GitHub credentials.
  campaigns	Endpoints to manage campaigns via the REST API.
  projects	Endpoints to manage Projects using the REST API.
  agent-tasks	Endpoints to manage and interact with agent tasks.
  agents	Endpoints for Agents secrets and variables.
